src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Geordie-Greep.-CREDIT_-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Archivio-Elena-Di-Vincenzo_Mondadori-Portfolio-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/geordie-greep">乔迪·格里普 (Geordie Greep)</a>邀请了热门歌曲《I Am Rectangular》的主唱肖恩·斯蒂芬斯 (Sean Stephens) 登台与他一起表演。看看下面的视频。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/geordie-greep-new-sound-album-review-black-midi-3799535">Geordie Greep – “新声音”评论：令人眼花缭乱的音乐性被大量的想法淹没</a></strong></li></ul><p>斯蒂芬斯于 2023 年首次凭借这首歌走红，<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CurV21OvhJk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">他长途跋涉到世界各地推广这</a>首歌，并在标志性旅游目的地的 TikTok 和 Instagram 上对口型同步这首歌。</p><p>尽管在网上遭到许多人的嘲笑，但它还是在前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-midi">Black Midi</a>主唱身上找到了粉丝，他之前<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@nts_radio/video/7428231408092515617" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在接受 NTS 广播电台采访时</a>谈到了他对这首“随机”曲目的钦佩。从那时起，他甚至<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@greepgreepgreep/video/7430228335881407776" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在表演时融入了即兴演奏</a>。</p><p>周五（1 月 24 日），格里普进一步激发了他对这一热门热门歌曲的兴趣，在纳什维尔的一场演出中欢迎斯蒂芬斯上台。</p><p>音乐会的片段显示，当格里普和他的乐队开始演奏“矩形”时，斯蒂芬斯走过人群。然后他爬上舞台，靠近麦克风，然后唱出标志性的开场白：“<em>我是长方形/我在骨头里感觉到它/我是长方形/我感觉没有洞</em>。”</p><p>看看下面。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFQpFPfvVBb/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.11